videos.headline: Porter powers in 1-yard TD
videos.description: Texas' Kyle Porter squeezes into the end-zone to cut deficit to 3.

videos.headline: Ertz throws laser to Schoen for TD
videos.description: Ertz and Schoen connect again for the passing touchdown to extend the Kansas State lead.

videos.headline: Ertz connects with Schoen for 82-yard TD
videos.description: Kansas State's Jesse Ertz finds Dalton Schoen over the middle for long touchdown strike.

videos.headline: Ehlinger finds Warren III wide open for TD
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger throws across his body to a wide-open Chris Warren III for the 33-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Texas scores on 1-yard TD run
videos.description: Kyle Porter bounces outside and waltzes into the end zone for his second touchdown of the game to take the lead over Kansas State.

videos.headline: Back-up QB runs in TD for Kansas State
videos.description: Alex Delton comes in for Jesse Ertz and sneaks in for the touchdown to tie the game at 24.

videos.headline: Texas strikes on first play of OT
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger finds Jerrod Heard up the middle for a wide-open touchdown to take the lead in OT.

videos.headline: K-State backup QB splits the defense for OT TD
videos.description: Alex Delton finds the hole and runs it in to send the game to the 2nd overtime.
